title: Wayne Rooney set to miss England qualifier against Estonia
text:
Wayne Rooney set to miss England qualifier against Estonia 08 Oct 2015 10:47:04 
comments 
England captain Wayne Rooney is set to miss England's Euro 2016 qualifier against Estonia through injury. 
For the third day in succession the 29-year-old forward was unable to train with his international team-mates after an ankle complaint sustained in Manchester United's defeat to Arsenal. 
Rooney is set to miss Friday's clash with Estonia as a result and is a major doubt for next week's trip to Lithuania in the Group E finale. Related Sport News
